parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the tire sidewall can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: Loud explosion or bang
sudden loss of air pressure
tire blows out
decreased control of the vehicle
tire failure with minimal wear.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Radiator Blockage and Oil Breather Tube Design
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The blockage of the radiator can cause the engine to overheat, leading to potential engine damage, breakdowns, and safety risks. The faulty design of the oil breather tube can contribute to the radiator blockage, exacerbating the issue.
symptoms: The engine overheats
the temperature gauge rises
the coolant fan does not function properly
oil and debris accumulate on the radiator.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Body Mount Failure Due to Loose Bolts
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of body mounts can cause the vehicle's body to detach from the frame, leading to loss of control, accidents, and safety risks.
symptoms: The body mounts rip off the frame
the vehicle's body shifts or detaches while driving
loose bolts are found on the body mounts.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Water Heater Pressure Relief Valve Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the pressure relief valve in the water heater can cause damage to the water heater and other components, leading to costly repairs and potential safety hazards.
symptoms: The water heater is not functioning properly
the air conditioning and heat thermostat need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the slide-out mechanism can cause damage to the vehicle's interior and exterior, making it difficult to use the living space.
symptoms: The large slide drifts when extended.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door hinge can cause damage to the door and surrounding components, making it difficult to open and close the door.
symptoms: Door hinge cracking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ice maker valve can cause water leaks and damage to the surrounding components.
symptoms: The ice maker valve would not open
and when it did open
there was a severe leak.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the refrigerator can cause food spoilage and inconvenience to the occupants.
symptoms: The refrigerator goes back and forth between AC and gas
then it either turns itself off or gives a trouble code in red letters.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the shower door can cause inconvenience and discomfort to the occupants.
symptoms: The shower door sticks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the bedroom window can cause inconvenience and discomfort to the occupants.
symptoms: The bedroom window is hard to close.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the propane detector can cause a false sense of security, potentially leading to safety hazards.
symptoms: The propane detector went off
and the consumer can't find out what set it off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the leveling jacks can cause the vehicle to be unstable, making it difficult to use the living space.
symptoms: The leveling jacks do not work.
